            "text",
            "{sc}caprice{/sc} {sc}whim{/sc} {sc}vagary{/sc} {sc}crotchet{/sc} mean an irrational or unpredictable idea or desire. {sc}caprice{/sc} stresses lack of apparent motivation and suggests willfulness. "
